		public static readonly string[] PerkDescription = { "Master the post-apocalypse! With your gun, aim at any Wasteland creature below your level and gain a chance to pacify it.", "Let Vault-Tec guide you! The path to your closest quest target is displayed in V.A.T.S.", "If nothing else, you can take a beating! Instantly gain +10 Damage Resistance", "What are you, part pack mule? Gain +25 to carry weight", "Stay on target! Hip-fire accuracy is improved when firing any gun.", "Catch some rays! Gain +2 to Strength and Endurance between the hours of 6:00a.m. and 6:00p.m.", "It's all about focus. You have improved control and can hold your breath longer when aiming with scopes.", "Become whisper, become shadow. You are 20% harder to detect while sneaking.", "You find more ammunition in containers.", "Waste not, want not! You can salvage uncommon components like screws, aluminum, and copper when scrapping weapons and armor.", "Take full advantage of advanced technology with access to base level and Rank 1 high-tech mods.", "You're part tree! While standing still, you gain +25 Damage Resistance and your melee and unarmed attacks deal 25% more damage.", "Machines will always serve humans, if you have anything to say about it. Hack a robot, and gain a chance to power it on or off, or initiate a self-destruct.", "Keep your distance long and your kill-count high. Attacks with non-automatic rifles do 20% more damage", "What goes around comes around! Any enemy's ranged attacks will sometimes ricochet back and instantly kill them. The closer you are to death, the higher the chance.", "You must be part mirror! Instantly gain +10 Energy Resistance.", "Exposure to the Wasteland has made you more resilient, instantly granting +10 Radiation Resistance.", "In combat, there's no time to hesitate. You can reload all guns faster.", "Your quick hands and sticky fingers make picking pockets 25% easier.", "There's no place to hide! In V.A.T.S you can target an enemy's body parts that are blocked by cover, with a decrease in accuracy.", "Nobody has a good time like you! There's no chance you'll get addicted to alcohol.", "Choo Choo! All aboard! While wearing Power Armor,sprinting into enemies hurts and staggers them. (Robots and oversized enemies are immune to the stagger.)", "You've learned to split the atom... and command it. Radiation weapons do 50% more damage and Fusion Cores last an extra 25% longer.", "Trained as a shadow warrior, your ranged sneak attack do 2.5x normal damage and your melee attacks do 4x normal damage.", "You are a creature of the night! Gain +2 to Intelligence and Perception between the hours of 6:00 p.m. and 6:00 a.m.", "Genius. Is. ANGRY! When your Health drops below 20%, time slows and you gain +20 Damage resistance and do 20% more damage while the effect lasts.", "Who is he? Why does he help? Who cares! The Mysterious Stranger will appear occasionally in V.A.T.S. to lend a hand, with deadly efficiency...", "They can't hurt what they can't hit! Get 25+ Damage Resistance and 25+ Energy Resistance when you're sprinting.", "As an agent of death, you can instantly kill a sleeping person. Your silenced weapons do an additional 15% sneak attack damage.", "Is there a doctor in the house? Stimpaks restore 40% of lost Health, and RadAway removes 40% of radiation.", "Who needs friends, anyway? When adventuring without a companion, you take 15% less damage and carry weight increases by 50.", "Your nimble fingers allow you to pick advanced locks.", "As the ruler everyone turns to, you are able to establish supply lines between your workshop settlements.", "You embody wellness! Instantly gain +20 maximum Health.", "Your digestive tract has adjusted to the weirdness of the Wasteland! Take less radiation from eating or drinking.", "You're charming... and dangerous. Men/Women suffer +5% damage in combat, and are easier to persuade in dialogue.", "Channel your chi to unleash devastating fury! Punching attacks do 20% more damage to your opponent.", "Time to show everyone who's boss! With your gun, aim at any human opponent below your level and gain a chance to pacify them.", "Because you lead by example, your companion does more damage in combat, and cannot hurt you.", "You're not stupid! Just... different. Randomly receive 3x XP from any action, and the lower your Intelligence, the greater the chance.", "Thanks to practice and conditioning, heavy guns do 20% more damage.", "Knowledge of cutting-edge computer encryption allows you to hack Advanced terminals", "Channel the spirit of the old west! Non-automatic pistols do 20% more damage.", "You gain access to base level and Rank 1 gun mods", "You've learned to apply ancient martial arts to gunplay! Do 25% more damage to your second V.A.T.S. target and beyond.", "Death becomes you! Any kill in V.A.T.S. has a 15% chance to restore all Action Points.", "Sure, you're still human - on the outside! Radiation now regenerates your lost Health.", "Feeling Lucky? You should! Each hit in V.A.T.S. has a chance of filling your Critical meter.", "You find more bottle caps in containers.", "The bigger the boom, the better! Your explosives do 25% more damage, and you can craft explosives at any Chemistry Station.", "You're a patient battlefield tactician, and can save a Critical Hit, to be used in V.A.T.S. when you need it most.", "Stay Focused! In V.A.T.S every attack on the same body part gains +10% accuracy.", "Rigorous combat training means automatic weapons do 20% more damage", "Any chems you take last 50% longer. Far out.", "All the rush without the hassle! You're 50% less likely to get addicted when consuming Chems", "You've mastered the art of the deal! Buying and selling prices at vendors are better.", "Feast on mortal flesh to heal your wounds! Eating human corpses restores Health.", "#ERROR!", "Find the gap and make the tackle! V.A.T.S. melee distance is increased significantly.", "Fire up the forge and gain access to base level and Rank 1 melee weapon mods.", "Swing for the fences! Do 20% more melee weapon damage.", "Advanced training for enhanced combat effectiveness! Criticals do 50% more extra damage.", "Get up close and personal! Gun bashing does 25% more damage.", "To defeat your enemies, know their weaknesses! You can view a target's specific damage resistances in V.A.T.S.", "Your faithful canine companion can hold an enemy, giving you a greater chance to hit them in V.A.T.S.", "Protect yourself from the dangers of the Wasteland with access to base level and Rank 1 armor mods.", "Water is your ally. You no longer take radiation damage from swimming, and can breathe underwater.", "Commune with beasts! With your gun, aim at any animal below your level and gain a chance to pacify it.", "Your skeleton has been infused with indestructible metal, reducing limb damage by 30%.", "There's no time to waste! Action Points regenerate 25% faster." };
